overview:
Daniel Frysinger is the Co-Founder of NOTCOT and the driver of the Concept, Architechture, and Business side of the site.

Daniel brings both a passion for elegant, intuitive interfaces and unparalleled technical expertise to Notcot.

Combining intuitive designs with their technical architecture comes naturally to Daniel, who holds degree in Cognitive Science (that’s right, he can get in your head), and in Dec 2007, gave up work as a designer and front-end engineer at a certain “very large” internet company, to pursue his passions through NOTCOT.

Source: NOTCOT.com
